{"tid":1459211,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"今晚風向 - 引起和理非勇武互屌","createTime":"2019-08-12T16:31:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T04:53:39.000Z","uid":13078,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e64cdf7b4bc52184932b848442cf1272d5f31622","tid":1459211,"uid":13078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:31:39.000Z","msg":"我知811大家見到有狗扮示威者會好不安 擔心前線已經比鬼滲透晒<br />\n但係我作為一個和理非都希望大家相信前線 唔係得冷氣軍師先識思考 佢地都識得獨立思考 <br />\n唔好再輕易話前線係鬼 咁樣做只會令前線心灰意冷 冇人再出黎幫和理非擋<br />\n見到有個post話衝立會義士係鬼都仲有咁多正評<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你地對唔對得住除埋口罩係立會讀宣言個位手足?</span></strong></span><br />\n而勇武手足亦都唔好再話和理非係散水撚啦 叫得和理非就梗係冇勇武咁大膽 特別係見到811嘅情況之後 佢地更加驚 和理非最大嘅作用就係人數 今日都見到人數多係可以即時癱瘓機場<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">大家唔好再互屌 有精力互屌不如集中火力5大訴求仲好!<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\n勇武同和理非同樣重要 請大家唔好互相分化!</span></strong></span><br />\n兄弟爬山 各有各做 是去是留 自己決定!</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1206449c30a9e251017c03abac6c1e436918869c","tid":1459211,"uid":13078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:31:59.000Z","msg":"推比手足睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9527edc0e8cbfa3623a7f15ef1a926e86cf85acc","tid":1459211,"uid":13078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:32:13.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"94dc02031a92dde9dfc6f15bf554c1bb5b5aaecc","tid":1459211,"uid":13078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:33:42.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"fa0a43c989c6d3dd30d7d96cc85e64bebcc442f6","tid":1459211,"uid":59666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e64cdf7b4bc52184932b848442cf1272d5f31622","tid":1459211,"uid":13078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:31:39.